\begin_layout Standard
If we decode by setting each bit to the maximum of its corresponding marginal,
 would we find the right codeword?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Answer: We would still be able to finf the right answer even if we decodes
 by setting each bit to the maximum of its corresponding marginal since
 the argmax value would be 0 for each character of the word.
\end_layout

